contentrichtext.text: '''Blomstedt''' is surname of: * [[Herbert Blomstedt]] (born 1927), a Swedish conductor * [[Jussi Jalas|Jussi Jalas, né Blomstedt]] (1908 - 1985), an accomplished Finnish conductor * [[Kaarlo Blomstedt|Kaarlo Viljanti Blomstedt]] (1880, Hämeenlinna, 1949 in Helsinki ), a Finnish historian and archivist * [[Yrjö Blomstedt|Yrjö Reinhold Emanuel Blomstedt]] (1926, Helsinki - 1994, Helsinki), a Finnish historian {{surname|Blomstedt}} [[Category:Swedish-language surnames]] [[Category:Surnames of Finnish origin]] {{Sweden-hist-stub}} {{surname-stub}}
